name: Zelda (Skyward Sword)
description:
So, am I done with Zeldas finally? Does anyone want Toon Zelda and Tetra? If no one says anything I'm just gonna go with no at least for now. I've made so many Zelda LoRAs....

Quirks:
It sometimes gives her extra hair ribbons.

Tips:
If you want the white dress version just add 'white dress' pretty simple

As Usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demos are Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 1.0
Last image is using the AbyssMaple model found here https://civitai.com/models/15316/abyssmaple

Next is Gumi. Then I'll take a look at the requests I got recently and pick one.
